<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar-collapse">
                <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;"><a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Iași Communities Guide</a></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-right" id="navbar-collapse">
        <% if (!user.name) { %>
            <span>Wanna be part of any of them? </span>
            <button class="btn btn-primary navbar-btn" id="login">Sign up</button>
        <% } else { %>
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                <li class="dropdown">
                    <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                        <img class="member hidden-xs" src="<%= user.avatar %>">
                        Welcome, <%= user.name %>!
                        <span class="caret"></span>
                    </a>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu" role="menu">
                        <% if (user && user.facebook && user.facebook.token) {%>
                        <li><a href="/unlink/facebook">Unlink Facebook</a></li>
                        <%} else { %>
                        <li><a href="/auth/facebook">Connect Facebook</a></li>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (user && user.twitter && user.twitter.token){ %>
                        <li><a href="/unlink/twitter">Unlink Twitter</a></li>
                        <%} else { %>
                        <li><a href="/auth/twitter">Connect Twitter</a></li>
                        <% } %>
                        <li class="divider"></li>
                        <li><a id="logout" href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<header class="container header">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1>Iași Communities Guide</h1>
            <p>Join one. Start one. Build something. No matter if it's purely technical, just for fun or sports oriented, sharing knowledge or passion is always worth it.</p>
            <p>Anything to be edited or do you want to include something on the list? Drop us a line at <a href='&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#111;&#102;&#102;&#105;&#99;&#101;&#64;&#110;&#111;&#110;&#46;&#114;&#111;'>&#111;&#102;&#102;&#105;&#99;&#101;&#64;&#110;&#111;&#110;&#46;&#114;&#111;</a> and we'll add it right up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="filters">
                <h4>Filter by topic:</h4>

                <button class="btn btn-default" data-filter="*">show all</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-filter=".technology">technology</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-filter=".management">management</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-filter=".creative">creative</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-filter=".fun">fun</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-filter=".educational">educational</button>
            </div>

            <div class="sorts">
                <h4>Sort list by:</h4>

                <button class="btn btn-default" data-sort="original-order">original order</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-sort="interest">topic</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-sort="alphabetical">alphabetical</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-sort="members">no. of members</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container isotope">
    <div class="row">
        <% for (var i=0; i<communities.length; i++) {%>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 item <%= communities[i].category.join(' ') %>" data-interest="<%= communities[i].category.join(', ') %>" data-members="<%= communities[i].memberList.length %>">
            <div class="visual">
                <% if (communities[i].photoURL) {%>
                <img src=<%=communities[i].photoURL%> >
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="description">
                <h3><%= communities[i].title %></h3>
                <p><%= communities[i].desc %></p>

                <h4>Find out more:</h4>
                <ul class="find-out-more list-inline">
                    <% if (communities[i].webLink) { %>
                    <li><a class="icon-link" href="<%= communities[i].webLink %>" target="_blank"></a></li>
                    <% } %>
                    <% if (communities[i].fbLink) {%>
                    <li><a class="icon-facebook" href="<%= communities[i].fbLink %>" target="_blank"></a></li>
                    <% } %>
                    <% if (communities[i].linkedinLink) {%>
                    <li><a class="icon-linkedin" href="<%= communities[i].linkedinLink %>" target="_blank"></a></li>
                    <% } %>
                    <% if (communities[i].meetupLink) {%>
                    <li><a class="icon-meetup" href="<%= communities[i].meetupLink %>" target="_blank"></a></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="members">
                <h4>Current supporters:</h4>
                <% if ( communities[i].memberList.length ) {
                    _.forEach(communities[i].memberList, function (member) {
                        isLeader = _.find(communities[i].leaders, function(leader) { return leader.toString() == member._id; })%>
                        <a class ="<%= isLeader ? 'leader' : '' %>" href="<%= member.profileUrl %>" target="_blank"><img class="member" title="<%= member.name %>" data-id="<%= member._id %>" src="<%= member.avatar %>"></a>
                <% })} else { %>
                    <span>Oh, no! No one has joined the party yet.</span>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <% isMember = _.find(user.communityList, function(community) { return community.toString() == communities[i]._id; }) %>
            <div class="actions">
                <a class="btn btn-primary join <%= isMember ? 'hidden' : '' %>" href="community/join/<%=communities[i]._id%>" data-communityId = <%=communities[i]._id%> >Support community!</a>
                <a class="btn btn-danger pull-right leave <%= isMember ? '' : 'hidden' %>" href="community/leave/<%=communities[i]._id%>" >Abandon team</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Tell us more about you</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Please login with one of your social media accounts in order to join the community.</p>
                    <p class="text-center">
                        <a href="/auth/facebook" class="btn btn-primary">Facebook</a>
                        <a href="/auth/twitter" class="btn btn-info">Twitter</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="container footer">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <p>Please keep in mind Communities Guide is merely a prototype. There are plenty of ideas for future development, we are quite sure you have some too. The source code is public on GitHub, don't be shy and contribute if you consider there's anything worth to be added.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <p>Communities Guide was built with <a href="http://getbootstrap.com" target="_blank">Bootstrap</a> and <a href="http://isotope.metafizzy.co" target="_blank">Isotope</a> over <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank">NodeJS</a>. Deployed to <a href="http://aws.amazon.com/elasticbeanstalk/" target="_blank">Amazon Elastic Beanstalk</a> by <a href="https://codeship.com" target="_blank">Codeship</a> from <a href="http://github.com" target="_blank">GitHub</a>. Playful endeavour by <a href="http://non.ro" target="_blank">NON</a>.</p>
            <div class="fb-share-button hidden-xs" data-href="http://iasi.communities.guide" data-layout="button_count"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

